description: Nestled on picturesque Lincoln Square! Beautifully renovated, Sundrenched East Side residence complete with 2 GARAGE PARKING spaces! Perfectly designed and extremely functional floor plan with two levels of living! Huge open main floor boasts a generous living area, separate dining space, a designer updated kitchen featuring SS appliances, granite counters, and a large breakfast island! Gas fireplace, custom bookshelves, and window seats plus a half bathroom complete this level. The upper level features a full bathroom, washer/dryer, and two bright & spacious bedrooms including a massive primary with en-suite bath. Private Roof Deck, Central Air + Hardwood floors throughout! This desirable boutique building offers recently renovated common areas, additional storage, a fitness room, and professional management. AAA location is just a few blocks from M Street Beach, Medal of Honor Park, and South Boston's local restaurants/shops. This home checks all of the boxes - Don't miss out!!!
